org.eclipse.scada.configuration.modbus

Interface ModbusMaster

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ModbusMasterImpl

    public interface ModbusMaster
    A representation of the model object 'Master'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Slaves
    • Endpoint
    • Id
    • Protocol Type
    • Inter Frame Delay

    See Also:
    ModbusPackage.getModbusMaster()
